{"tid":1870267,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"黑龍江一罩難求　倡民眾交出N95換5個醫用口罩","createTime":"2020-02-08T17:00:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-08T19:16:06.000Z","uid":81228,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"a23df7d15a635177180ca9e1f606678c007f55e1","tid":1870267,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T17:00:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20200208/_2020020822531527584.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20200208%2F_2020020822531527584.jpg&h=e9e01bec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n因疫情爆發，全球口罩供不應求。<br />\n<br />\n自武漢肺炎爆發後，內地不少地方醫療物資出現短缺，N95口罩更是「一罩難求」。黑龍江政府近日發佈公告，為保障醫護人員安全，緩解全省醫用防護口罩庫存緊張局面，省應對疫情指揮部倡議，全省民眾用醫用防護口罩（或符合N95/KN95及以上標準顆粒物防護口罩）置換一次性醫用口罩呼籲全省民眾用1個N95口罩換5個一次性醫用口罩。<br />\n<br />\n據公告顯示，置換口罩活動率先在中省直各單位開展，由相關單位組織幹部職工根據個人意願，按照1:5比例進行口罩置換（1隻醫用防護口罩置換5隻一次性使用医用口罩），並由各單位統一登記回收後，交付省應對疫情指揮部物資保障組置換。<br />\n<br />\n針對口罩短缺問題，吉林、浙江兩省也對公職人員使用N95口罩作出限制，禁止全省各級黨政領導幹部、公務員及各類公職人員購買和使用N95口罩。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hd.stheadline.com/nocv/news-detail.php?r=1197146&amp;y=2020\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnocv%2Fnews-detail.php%3Fr%3D1197146%26y%3D2020&d=CEXeqV9R6719hdRRqmVjOpszS%2Fgy1fqSqMk7TcT3QhU%3D&h=39743d13\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnocv%2Fnews-detail.php%3Fr%3D1197146%26y%3D2020&h=b2531b3b\" target=\"_blank\">https://hd.stheadline.com/nocv/news-detail.php?r=1197146&amp;y=2020</a>"},{"pid":"f6aa204efcae90536daebe0cfce4dbc5122df2e5","tid":1870267,"uid":158613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T17:13:26.000Z","msg":"你現身處支那"},{"pid":"96f6ea8a6e1f5ee5fea3a30e206f93f7ef7a3715","tid":1870267,"uid":44074,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T17:16:50.000Z","msg":"用支那人嘅諗法<br />\n應該會用完個n95口罩先攞去換<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a53131fd06149512ebd7378d94b297b1bde250c5","tid":1870267,"uid":195444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T18:53:26.000Z","msg":"香港啲口罩終於有着落<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77a89aa292325687acbcf432aa4acde7925b79a5","tid":1870267,"uid":46321,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"96f6ea8a6e1f5ee5fea3a30e206f93f7ef7a3715","tid":1870267,"uid":44074,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T17:16:50.000Z","msg":"用支那人嘅諗法<br />\n應該會用完個n95口罩先攞去換<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T18:55:41.000Z","msg":"冇所謂啦，嗰5個普通罩咪又係用過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e889899d75afa45f154556c56da721c9e9559e49","tid":1870267,"uid":37869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"77a89aa292325687acbcf432aa4acde7925b79a5","tid":1870267,"uid":46321,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"96f6ea8a6e1f5ee5fea3a30e206f93f7ef7a3715","tid":1870267,"uid":44074,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T17:16:50.000Z","msg":"用支那人嘅諗法<br />\n應該會用完個n95口罩先攞去換<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T18:55:41.000Z","msg":"冇所謂啦，嗰5個普通罩咪又係用過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T19:08:04.000Z","msg":"口罩產量大增<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66cd2e24d653337f3bd91f285603c4bd7485f120","tid":1870267,"uid":323132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T19:16:06.000Z","msg":"支那人交N95同條命出黎 換黎公安有5個口罩加一個N95"}]}